VALUES
  ('dietitian-moex-02593', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-105-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於飯後血糖上升，同時脂肪酸的代謝也會受到調節，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["細胞內的［NADH］／［NAD+］比例上升，會抑制 β-羥基乙醯－輔酶 A 去氫酶（β-hydroxyacyl-CoA dehydrogenase）進而抑制脂肪酸的β-氧化作用", "丙二醯－輔酶A（malonyl-CoA）的生成會抑制糖解作用之進行，過多的糖可轉成三酸甘油酯貯存起來", "胰島素的分泌具有活化乙醯－輔酶A羧化酶（acetyl-CoA carboxylase）之作用", "肉鹼醯基轉移酶（carnitine acyltransferase）會受抑制，以確保脂肪酸不會進入細胞質而進行氧化反應"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "dbdc7430cd09", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f7bdd424f961", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105030", "c": "103", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次中醫師分階段、營養師心理師護理師社工師考試", "original_question_number": 26, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-02594', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-105-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種化合物可能是必需脂肪酸的代謝產物？', '["油酸（oleic acid）", "棕櫚烯酸（palmitoleic acid）", "花生四烯酸（arachidonic acid）", "乳酸（lactic acid）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "dbdc7430cd09", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f7bdd424f961", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105030", "c": "103", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次中醫師分階段、營養師心理師護理師社工師考試", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-02595', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-105-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '細胞膜的結構特稱為流體鑲嵌模型（fluid mosaic model），關於此模型之敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["膜中的脂肪與蛋白質成分並存，並不會相互反應生成中間物質", "穿越細胞膜的蛋白質可在膜內外移動，且不具方向性", "蛋白質在脂雙層上，可以沿著膜作平面移動", "細胞膜的脂雙層可以進行橫向運動（lacteral motion）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "dbdc7430cd09", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f7bdd424f961", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105030", "c": "103", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次中醫師分階段、營養師心理師護理師社工師考試", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
